&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;314&quot; data-end=&quot;386&quot;&gt;Ready to accelerate your career?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;563&quot; data-end=&quot;823&quot;&gt;Clara is the fastest-growing company in Latin America. We&#39;ve built the leading solution for companies to make and manage all their payments. We already help over 20,000 large and growing businesses operate with agility and financial clarity through locally issued corporate cards, bill pay, financing, and a powerful B2B platform built for scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;563&quot; data-end=&quot;823&quot;&gt;Clara is backed by some of the most successful investors in the world, including top regional VCs like monashees, Kaszek, and Canary, and leading global funds like Notable Capital, Coatue, DST Global Partners, ICONIQ Growth, General Catalyst, Citi Ventures, SV Angel, Citius, Endeavor Catalyst, and Goldman Sachs - in addition to dozens of angel investors and local family offices.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We’re building the financial infrastructure that powers high-performing organizations across the region. We invite you to join us if you want to be part of a fast-paced environment that will accelerate your career and support you to do some of the best work of your life alongside a passionate and committed team distributed across the Americas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for an &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;21&quot;&gt;Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt;. At Clara, our mission is to empower organizations to operate with agility and transparency. As a key driver of our growth in the Brazilian market, you will accelerate Clara’s expansion within the SaaS Expense Management and Fintech space.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;In this role, you will lead the outbound effort to modernize how Brazilian companies handle corporate spending. You will identify and convert high-potential prospects that currently rely on legacy banking or fragmented expense tools. This is a hunter position: you will own the full sales cycle, from initial prospecting to contract signing, navigating the specific complexities of the Brazilian financial ecosystem to deliver Clara’s integrated solution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,0,0&quot;&gt;Drive the outbound sales motion for Clara’s accounts payable module and related financial workflow solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,1,0&quot;&gt;Lead the go-to-market strategy in the tech industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,2,0&quot;&gt;Identify and engage companies using legacy financial processes, positioning Clara as the integrated alternative to traditional banks and manual expense tools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot;&gt;Generate a high volume of qualified leads through proactive prospecting and strategic outreach via &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;5,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;99&quot;&gt;Amplemarket&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,4,0&quot;&gt;Manage a robust pipeline of mid-market and enterprise clients, focusing on long-term scalability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5,5,0&quot;&gt;Influence Finance Directors, CFOs, and Controllers by demonstrating a deep understanding of financial workflows, reconciliation, and ERP integration.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;314&quot; data-end=&quot;386&quot;&gt;Ready to accelerate your career?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;563&quot; data-end=&quot;823&quot;&gt;Clara is the fastest-growing company in Latin America. We&#39;ve built the leading solution for companies to make and manage all their payments. We already help over 20,000 large and growing businesses operate with agility and financial clarity through locally issued corporate cards, bill pay, financing, and a powerful B2B platform built for scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;563&quot; data-end=&quot;823&quot;&gt;Clara is backed by some of the most successful investors in the world, including top regional VCs like monashees, Kaszek, and Canary, and leading global funds like Notable Capital, Coatue, DST Global Partners, ICONIQ Growth, General Catalyst, Citi Ventures, SV Angel, Citius, Endeavor Catalyst, and Goldman Sachs - in addition to dozens of angel investors and local family offices.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We’re building the financial infrastructure that powers high-performing organizations across the region. We invite you to join us if you want to be part of a fast-paced environment that will accelerate your career and support you to do some of the best work of your life alongside a passionate and committed team distributed across the Americas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;20&quot;&gt;Working Capital &amp;amp; Cash Management Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt; to accelerate the growth of the company’s portfolio through the prospecting, structuring, and closing of B2B deals. In this role, you will offer financial working capital solutions and transactional tools (&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;281&quot;&gt;Cash Management&lt;/strong&gt;) that optimize our clients&#39; cash flow cycles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;Your primary responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Origination and Prospecting:&lt;/strong&gt; Actively identify and acquire new medium and large enterprises that require financing for their daily operations or modernizations of their treasury setups.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Credit Structuring:&lt;/strong&gt; Design short-term credit proposals (revolving lines, simple loans, factoring) tailored to the client’s accounts receivable (AR) and accounts payable (AP) needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Cash Management Sales:&lt;/strong&gt; Position key transactional solutions, such as payment dispersion platforms (for suppliers and payroll) and advanced collection and reconciliation systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Committee Defense:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with the analysis team to prepare and defend commercial and risk proposals before the Credit Committee to secure formal approvals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Cross-selling:&lt;/strong&gt; Increase the profitability of each acquired client by seamlessly integrating more of Clara&#39;s corporate products into their daily financial operation

