&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;Your primary responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Large Fleet Prospecting:&lt;/strong&gt; Actively identify and close corporate accounts (distribution companies, last-mile delivery, field services, manufacturing) operating medium to large vehicle fleets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Consultative Mobility Sales:&lt;/strong&gt; Evaluate the client&#39;s current fuel dispersion and travel expense processes to demonstrate the return on investment (ROI) of using Clara through parameter controls, dynamic limits, and real-time visibility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Operations &amp;amp; Finance Negotiation:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead complex sales committees, successfully aligning the Director of Logistics (focused on daily operations) with the Director of Finance (focused on cash flow and tax deductibility).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Driving Adoption:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure that once a contract is signed, cards and platform access are correctly distributed and utilized by drivers and route managers to maximize Total Payment Volume (TPV).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
