&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;Our strategic focus is capturing Share of Wallet; we are not looking for a screen operator or trader, but a high-level B2B business originator who leverages technical advantages and competitive exchange rates to move existing corporate flows into our ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
